OL,3,EIF COKE IS A MYSTERYG``````````````````
OL,4,G                                       
OL,5,GI own an Atari 2600 game console and   
OL,6,Ghave a Parker cartridge, Action Force, 
OL,7,Gfor it.                                
OL,9,GHowever, I've tried everywhere to get  
OL,10,Git repaired, but no luck so far. Do you
OL,11,Ghave any suggestions?                  
OL,13,BMark Holbrook, Castleford              
OL,15,FYes. Call the Computer Cavern on 01628 
OL,16,F891 101, and ask to speak to Richard   
OL,17,FGandy, or his son, "Half Beard".       
