OL,3,EAND MICHAEL JACKSON... HISTORYG````````
OL,4,G                                       
OL,5,GOh dear, oh dear! You boys at Digi have
OL,6,Gsurpassed yourselves - "we'd bet our   
OL,7,Glives on Shocker never being released  
OL,8,Gin this country".                      
OL,10,GWell, you now know it's at the         
OL,11,GTrocadero, London. For a punishment,   
OL,12,Gput on your puffy jackets (I know you  
OL,13,Gall own them) and go to the Trocadero  
OL,14,Gand sit on Shocker for a day or so!    
OL,15,BMike Hunt, feeling very smug           
OL,17,FYes, yes. Alright. But the Trocadero is
OL,18,Fonly ONE place, man. We've yet to see a
OL,19,FShocker in our local chip shop.        
