OL,3,EIF BEAUTY IS TRUTH AND SURGERYG````````
OL,5,GAll your letters talk about wanting    
OL,6,Goriginal games, but it's not possible  
OL,7,Gto design playable, original games too 
OL,8,Goften. Fighting, driving and shooting  
OL,9,Gare what people want to play, not a    
OL,10,Gsheep dog simulator. If your readers   
OL,11,Gare so clever, why don't they suggest  
OL,12,Goriginal games ideas?                  
OL,13,BThe Sad Lord, Nottingham               
OL,15,FYes, but what's so wrong with wanting  
OL,16,Foriginal fighting, driving and shooting
OL,17,Fgames, instead of cheap copies?        
